annotationA: NHP2-like protein 1 homolog; Binds to the 5'-stem-loop of U4 snRNA and may play a role in the late stage of spliceosome assembly. The protein undergoes a conformational change upon RNA-binding (By similarity)
annotationB: La protein homolog; May be involved in transcription termination by RNA polymerase III. Binds RNA and DNA. Binds to precursors of RNA polymerase III transcripts. May play a specialized role during fly development
